Introduction

Cho Kyu Hyun is the main vocalist and maknae of the boy group Super Junior and its sub-units Super Junior K.R.Y and Super Junior-M under Label SJ, a subsidiary of SM Entertainment. He debuted as a solo artist in 2014 with his album "At Gwanghwamun".
